# Cloudflare R2 / Pages Functions
# These are NOT needed in .env — they are set as server-side
# environment variables in the Cloudflare Dashboard:
#   FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID        — your Firebase project ID
#   DOWNLOAD_SIGNING_SECRET    — random 64-char hex secret for HMAC-signed download URLs
#   ZAVU_BUCKET (R2 binding)   — configured in wrangler.toml
